text: Maria Dolgikh Maria Dolgikh (born July 24, 1987) is a Russian table tennis player. She competed at the 2016 Summer Olympics in the women's singles event, in which she was eliminated in the first round by Jian Fang Lay. ==References== Category:1987 births Category:Living people Category:Russian female table tennis players Category:Olympic table tennis players of Russia Category:Table tennis players at the 2016 Summer Olympics
